OL,3,CWatch: Moment proxy bomb explodes at
OL,4,CDunmurry police station
OL,6,FThe PSNI has released bodycam footage
OL,7,Fof the moment a car bomb detonated
OL,8,Foutside Dunmurry police station on
OL,9,FSaturday night.
OL,11,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher described
OL,12,Fthe attack as "deliberate, reckless
OL,13,Fand stupid".
OL,15,FA male delivery driver was hijacked in
OL,16,Fthe Twinbrook area of west Belfast, a
OL,17,Fdevice placed inside the vehicle, and
OL,18,Fhe was ordered to drive to Dunmurry
OL,19,Fpolice station.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
