PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777317067
OL,3,CWatch: Moment proxy bomb explodes at
OL,4,CDunmurry police station
OL,6,FThe car exploded outside the station
OL,7,Fas people were being evacuated, in an
OL,8,Fincident which is being treated by
OL,9,Fpolice as attempted murder.
OL,11,FIt is the second such attack in less
OL,12,Fthan a month, after Lurgan police
OL,13,Fstation was targeted.
OL,15,FThe First and deputy First Ministers
OL,16,Fstood alongside the chief constable in
OL,17,Funited condemnation of the attack,
OL,18,Fsuspected to be carried out by the New
OL,19,FIRA.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
