OL,3,CWatch: Moment proxy bomb explodes at
OL,4,CDunmurry police station
OL,6,FThere was also round condemnation of
OL,7,Fthe incident in the House of Commons
OL,8,Ffollowing an urgent question to the
OL,9,FSecretary of State by Alliance MP
OL,10,FSorcha Eastwood on Monday afternoon.
OL,12,FHilary Benn blamed a "small number of
OL,13,Fpeople who represent no one but
OL,14,Fthemselves".
